\c 13
\s UJesu ufundisa ngokuphenduka
\p
\v 1 Njalo ngalesosikhathi kwaba khona abathile abamtshela ngamaGalili, igazi lawo uPilatu alixubanisa lemihlatshelo yawo\x + 3.1.\x*.
\v 2 UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Licabanga ukuthi amaGalili la ayeyizoni yini kulawo wonke amaGalili, ngoba ahlupheka izinto ezinje?
\v 3 Hatshi bo, ngithi kini: Kodwa uba lingaphenduki, lizabhubha ngokunjalo lonke\x + Seb. 28.4.\x*.
\v 4 Lalabo abalitshumi lesificaminwembili, owawela phezu kwabo umphotshongo eSilowama wababulala, licabanga ukuthi bona babebabi\f + \fk ababi: \fl Gr. \fq abalezikwelede.\f* yini kulabantu bonke ababehlala eJerusalema?
\v 5 Hatshi bo, ngithi kini: Kodwa uba lingaphenduki, lizabhubha ngokunjalo lonke\x + Neh. 3.15.\x*.
\s Umfanekiso womkhiwa ongatheliyo
\p
\v 6 Wasekhuluma lumfanekiso \add wathi\add*: \add Umuntu\add* othile wayelomkhiwa owawuhlanyelwe esivinini sakhe; wafika edinga isithelo kuwo, kodwa ka\add si\add*tholanga\x + Mat. 21.19. Mark. 11.13. Isa. 5.2.\x*.
\v 7 Wasesithi kuso isisebenzi sesivini: Khangela, sekuyiminyaka emithathu ngisiza ngidinga isithelo emkhiweni, kodwa nginga\add si\add*tholi; ugamule; yini ukuthi wone ngitsho umhlabathi\x + Mat. 3.10.\x*?
\v 8 Sasesiphendula sathi kuye: Nkosi, ake uwuyekele langalumnyaka, ngize ngigebhe ngiwugombolozele, ngithele umquba;
\v 9 njalo uba uthela isithelo, \add kuhle\x + 2 Lan. 2.3. Luka 19.42. Gen. 30.27.\x*\add*; kodwa uba kunge\add njalo\add*, emva kwalokho uzawugamula\x + Mat. 3.10.\x*.
\s Ukusiliswa kowesifazana ngesabatha
\p
\v 10 Futhi wayefundisa kwelinye lamasinagoge ngesabatha;
\v 11 njalo khangela, kwakukhona owesifazana owayelomoya wobuthakathaka iminyaka elitshumi leyisificaminwembili\x + Seb. 16.16. 1 Joha. 4.6. Luka 12.16.\x*, esegogekile, wayengalulami ngokupheleleyo\x + 21.28.\x*.
\v 12 Kwathi uJesu embona wa\add m\add*bizela kuye, wathi kuye: Mama, ukhululwe ebuthakathakeni bakho.
\v 13 Wasebeka izandla phezu kwakhe\x + Mat. 9.18. Mark. 5.23; 6.5; 7.32; 8.23,25. 16.18. 4.40. Seb. 9.12,17; 28.8.\x*; njalo wahle welulanyiswa\x + Heb. 12.12.\x*, wadumisa uNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 15.31.\x*.
\v 14 Kodwa umphathi wesinagoge\x + Mark. 5.22.\x*, ethukuthele ngoba uJesu esilise ngesabatha\x + Joha. 5.10.\x*, waphendula wathi exukwini: Zikhona insuku eziyisithupha okufanele ukusetshenzwa ngazo\x + Eks. 20.9.\x*; ngakho wozani ngazo lisiliswe, kodwa kungabi ngosuku lwesabatha\x + 14.3. Mat. 12.10.\x*.
\v 15 Ngakho iNkosi yamphendula, yathi: Mzenzisi\x + Mat. 7.5. Luka 6.42.\x*, ngulowo lalowo wenu kayikhululi yini inkabi yakhe kumbe ubabhemi\x + 14.5.\x* esibayeni ngesabatha, a\add yi\add*khokhele aye\add yi\add*nathisa\x + 2.7.\x*?
\v 16 Lalo, oyindodakazi kaAbrahama\x + 19.9.\x*, uSathane obembophile, khangela, iminyaka elitshumi leyisificaminwembili, kakufanele yini ukuthi akhululwe kulesisibopho ngosuku lwesabatha\x + Seb. 16.16. 1 Joha. 4.6. Luka 13.16.\x*?
\v 17 Kwathi esitsho lezizinto, bayangeka bonke ababephikisana laye; lexuku lonke lathokoza ngezinto zonke ezilodumo ezenziwe nguye\x + 18.43.\x*.
\s Umfanekiso wenhlanyelo yemasitedi, lowemvubelo
\p
\v 18 Wasesithi\x + Mat. 13.31-33. Luka 13.18,19. Mark. 4.30-32.\x*: Umbuso kaNkulunkulu unjengani? Futhi ngizawufananisa lani?
\v 19 Unjengohlamvu lwemasitedi, umuntu aluthatha wa\add lu\add*phosa esivandeni sakhe; lwaselumila, lwaba yisihlahla esikhulu, lenyoni zezulu zakhele engatsheni zaso\x + 13.20. Mat. 11.16.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Wasebuya wathi: Ngizawufananisa lani umbuso kaNkulunkulu?
\v 21 Unjengemvubelo, ayithathayo owesifazana wayifaka ezilinganisweni ezintathu zempuphu, kwaze kwabila konke\x + 13.20. Mat. 11.16.\x*.
\s UJesu ukhuluma ngendlela yempilo
\p
\v 22 Wasehamba edabula imizi lemizana efundisa\x + Mark. 6.6.\x*, ejonge ukuya eJerusalema\x + 9.51,53. 17.11. 19.28.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Omunye wasesithi kuye: Nkosi, balutshwana yini abasindiswayo\x + Seb. 2.47. 1 Kor. 1.18. 2 Kor. 2.15. Isam. 21.24.\x*? Wasesithi kubo:
\v 24 Zamani kakhulu ukungena ngesango elincinyane; ngoba abanengi, ngithi kini, bazadinga ukungena, kodwa bazakwehluleka\x + Joha. 18.36. 1 Kor. 9.25. Kol. 1.29. 4.12. 1 Tim. 6.12. 2 Tim. 4.7.\x*\x + Mat. 7.13.\x*.
\v 25 Emva kokuthi umninindlu\x + Isa. 55.6.\x* esesukume wavala umnyango\x + Mat. 25.10.\x*, beseliqala ukuma ngaphandle liqoqode emnyango, lisithi: Nkosi, Nkosi, sivulele\x + Mat. 25.11.\x*; yena-ke aphendule athi kini: Kangilazi, lapho elivela khona\x + 13.27. Mat. 7.23. 25.12.\x*;
\v 26 lapho lizaqala ukuthi: Sadla sanatha phambi kwakho\x + 5.29. 7.36. 14.1.\x*, njalo wawufundisa emigwaqweni yakithi\x + 13.22.\x*.
\v 27 Kodwa uzakuthi: Ngithi kini: Kangilazi lapho elivela khona\x + 13.27. Mat. 7.23. 25.12.\x*; sukani kimi lina lonke benzi bokubi\x + Hlab. 6.8.\x*.
\v 28 Lapho kuzakuba khona ukukhala lokugedla amazinyo\x + Mat. 8.12.\x*, nxa selibona uAbrahama loIsaka loJakobe labaprofethi bonke embusweni kaNkulunkulu, kodwa lina lilahlelwe ngaphandle\x + Mat. 8.11.\x*.
\v 29 Futhi bazakuza\x + Mat. 8.11.\x* bevela empumalanga lentshonalanga, njalo enyakatho leningizimu, bahlale embusweni kaNkulunkulu\x + Isam. 21.13.\x*.
\v 30 Njalo khangelani, bakhona abokucina abazakuba ngabokuqala, njalo bakhona abokuqala abazakuba ngabokucina\x + Mat. 19.30.\x*.
\s Ukuzonda kukaHerodi
\p
\v 31 Ngelanga elifananayo kwafika abaFarisi abathile, bathi kuye: Phuma usuke lapha\x + Mat. 19.1. Mark. 10.1.\x*, ngoba uHerodi ufuna ukukubulala\x + 3.1.\x*.
\v 32 Wasesithi kubo: Hambani lilitshele lelokhanka: Khangela, ngiyakhupha amadimoni ngenza izelapho lamuhla lakusasa, langelesithathu ngipheleliswe\x + Heb. 2.10. 5.9. 7.28. Heb. 11.40. 12.23.\x*.
\v 33 Kodwa kumele ukuthi ngihambe lamuhla lakusasa\x + Joha. 11.9.\x* langomhlomunye\x + Seb. 20.15. 21.26.\x*; ngoba kakwenzeki\x + 17.1.\x* ukuthi umprofethi abulawelwe ngaphandle kweJerusalema\x + Mat. 5.12.\x*.
\s UJesu ukhalela iJerusalema
\p
\v 34 Jerusalema, Jerusalema, wena obulala abaprofethi, lobakhanda ngamatshe labo abathunywe kuwe! Bengithanda kangakanani ukubuthela ndawonye abantwana bakho\x + 13.34,35. Mat. 23.37-39.\x*, njengesikhukhukazi \add sibuthela\add* amatsiyane aso ngaphansi kwempiko, kodwa kalivumanga\x + Mat. 23.37.\x*.
\v 35 Khangelani, indlu yenu itshiywe kini ilunxiwa\x + Hlab. 69.25. Levi 26.31,32. Isa. 1.7. Mika 3.12.\x*; njalo ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Kalisoze langibona kuze kufike ukuthi lithi: Ubusisiwe ozayo ebizweni leNkosi\x + Hlab. 118.26. Mat. 21.9. 23.39. Mark. 11.9. Luka 19.38. Joha. 12.13.\x*.
